Path2KML

Class BuildFolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • Path2KML.BuildFolder

  • public class BuildFolder
extends java.lang.Object
    This class create folder with data information from CSV file and turn it to KML. Folder include all points of project. Here we must to create GIS project from CSV file.
